{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, keyframes are obtained based on the ordering of importance.",
    "In summary, the contributions of this paper are as follows.• We propose a paradigm called keyframe recommendation based on feature intersection and fusion to solve the keyframe extraction problem.",
    "This paradigm introduces the approach of recommendation algorithms for processing structured textual data to visual data.",
    "• We propose an algorithm for jointly extracting intra-frame image features based on multiple image descriptors and an algorithm for jointly extracting inter-frame distance features based on multiple distance calculation methods.",
    "The algorithm comprehensively describes the frame by constructing rich image features for each frame using multiple descriptors and describes the video sequence by calculating inter-frame distance features."
  ]
}